cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.SI

The paper deals with the analysis of deep neural networks, specifically denoising autoencoders, and their transportation dynamics. This topic falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) as well as information theory (cs.IT) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the application of transportation analysis in computer vision (cs.CV) and systems and control (cs.SI).
